    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power curve up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing aluminum lower control arms and multi-link rear architecture for superior lateral grip and transient response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain and chassis integrity are optimized for immediate performance use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
