      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances reliability with a clean aesthetic. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear quarter panel. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and impressively preserved; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, featuring a smooth-idling engine and crisp gear shifts. It has a documented service history, including a recent cooling system flush and a fresh oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that has been driven with care and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 32500.0,
